#  To-Do CLI App

A simple and fast command-line To-Do List app built with Python.  
Easily add, view, complete, and delete tasks from your terminal.

---

##  Features

-  Add new tasks
-  List all tasks
-  Mark tasks as done
-  Delete tasks
-  Auto-generated unique IDs
-  Timestamped entries
-  Tasks saved in a CSV file

